{
    "poem_title": "- 72 - ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Lope de Vega",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Si Atenas tus pinceles conociera,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "¿qué poca gloria diera a Apolodoro,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "ni en Pario mármol ilustrara el oro",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "el nombre a Zeuxis, que a tus obras diera?",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si Atenas tus pinceles conociera,\n¿qué poca gloria diera a Apolodoro,\nni en Pario mármol ilustrara el oro\nel nombre a Zeuxis, que a tus obras diera?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Parnasio en la palestra se rindiera,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "como en el grave estilo Metrodoro;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "ni pluma se atreviera a tu decoro,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "sólo pintarte tu pincel pudiera.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Parnasio en la palestra se rindiera,\ncomo en el grave estilo Metrodoro;\nni pluma se atreviera a tu decoro,\nsólo pintarte tu pincel pudiera."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Bien pueden tus colores alabarse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "y el arte de tu ingenio peregrino,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "cuanto puede imitar docta cultura.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--++--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bien pueden tus colores alabarse,\ny el arte de tu ingenio peregrino,\ncuanto puede imitar docta cultura."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "Que si al cielo quisiera retratarse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "sólo fiara a tu pincel divino",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+----+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "la inmensa perfección de su hermosura.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que si al cielo quisiera retratarse,\nsólo fiara a tu pincel divino\nla inmensa perfección de su hermosura."
        }
    ]
}